title: Big Brother Australia - Daily Show 1
description:
Big Brother Australia - Daily Show 1.mp4 (484.77 megabyte)

New presenters; out with Gretel and in with Kyle and Jackie O. A more diverse range of contestants; Nanna Terri is a bit of a worry, but if Jackie O gets her way, she&#039;ll be sharing a blanket (yep folks, there&#039;s only one), with her hero, Pauline Hanson. But the concept&#039;s the same. Take a bunch of misfits and watch them try to fit in.
